# License

## Suggested Citation

If you use WBOPENDATA in your research, please cite it as follows:

**APA Format:**
> Azevedo, J. P. (2025). WBOPENDATA: Stata module to access World Bank databases (v17.4) [Computer software]. Retrieved from https://github.com/jpazvd/wbopendata

**BibTeX:**
```bibtex
@software{azevedo2025wbopendata,
  title={WBOPENDATA: Stata module to access World Bank databases},
  author={Azevedo, Jo{\~a}o Pedro},
  year={2025},
  version={17.4},
  url={https://github.com/jpazvd/wbopendata}
}
```

**Stata Format:**
```
Azevedo, J. P. (2025). WBOPENDATA: Stata module to access World Bank databases, version 17.4. 
Retrieved from https://github.com/jpazvd/wbopendata
```

For the most current citation information, see [CITATION.cff](CITATION.cff).

